      <h2 id="special-thoughts-on-healing-after-losing-a-pet">Special Thoughts on Healing After Losing a Pet</h2>
      <p></p>
<p>The healing process is unique to each person, but remembering the positive impact of the pet and allowing oneself to grieve are essential.</p>
<p>Allow yourself time to grieve.  There's no timetable for healing.  Remember the joy, laughter, and unconditional love your pet brought into your life.  These memories, as bittersweet as they may be, will eventually become a source of comfort, reminding you of the special bond you shared.  Embrace the healing process, and know that the love you shared will forever remain in your heart.</p>
    
  
